# Django Group File Sharing App

A Django web application that allows users to:

- Create accounts
- Create and join groups
- Upload and download files inside groups
- Send messages to groups
- Join groups by id

## Tech stack
- Python
- Django
- SQLite (development)
- HTML, CSS, JS

## Setup

pip install django
python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py runserver

#KEEP IN MIND

The method used to login users is not profetional
nor secure, you should use django's build in login
function and user model.

You should also use a PostgreSQL database or any
other profetional database if you want to deploy an
actual app.
